# LawEZY Monorepo - Comprehensive Production Gitignore

# === 🛡️ Institutional Security ===
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
secrets.json
*.pem
*.key

# === 💻 IDE / System ===
.vscode/
.idea/
.classpath
.project
.settings/
*.iml
*.log
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# === ☕ Java / Backend (LawEZY-Backend) ===
**/target/
**/*.class
**/*.jar
**/*.war
**/*.nar
**/*.ear
**/*.zip
**/*.tar.gz
**/*.rar
**/build/
.mvn/
**/bin/

# === ⚛️ React / Frontend (LawEZY-Client) ===
**/node_modules/
**/dist/
**/build/
**/out/
.vite/
npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
.pnp*
.eslintcache

# === 🟢 Node.js (LawEZY-Messenger) ===
# (Covered by node_modules pattern above)
**/logs/
**/pids/
*.pid
*.seed
*.pid.lock

# === 🐍 Python (LawEZY-AI-Service) ===
**/venv/
**/env/
**/ENV/
**/__pycache__/
**/*.py[cod]
**/*$py.class
**/.pytest_cache/
**/.python-version
**/.venv
**/pip-log.txt
**/pip-delete-this-directory.txt

# === 🗄️ Database / Local State ===
**/h2_db/
**/db-data/
**/mongo-data/
**/dump.rdb
